cast.overview: A raw and emotionally revealing look at one of the most iconic artists of our time during a transformational period in her life as she learns to embrace her role not only as a songwriter and performer, but as a woman harnessing the full power of her voice.
cast.title: Miss Americana

details.biography: Jade Jolie is the stage name of Josh Green, a reality television personality, drag queen, and celebrity impersonator. They rose to prominence after competing on the fifth season of Logo TV's reality competition television series RuPaul's Drag Race.  On September 8, 2021 it was announced that Jade would appear on the fourth season of The Boulet Brothers' Dragula.
details.name: Jade Jolie
